-- MBIA closes $1.1 billion share offer
-- 
-- Wed Feb 13, 2008 6:14pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/02/13/us-mbia-shares-idUSWNAS093620080213

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - MBIA Inc ( MBI.N ) said on Wednesday it closed the sale of $1.1 billion of shares, or $100,000 more than previously announced, after underwriters exercised their right to sell more shares. 

 MBIA said it sold 236.2 million shares at $12.15 apiece. (Reporting by  Dan Wilchins , editing by Richard Chang)